quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  88,1,hl 'atak -ayha alrswl- khabar alqiamat alty tghsha alnaas bahwalha?
  88,2,"wjwh alkufaar yawmayidh dhlylt baledhab, mjhdt bialeamal mtebt, tsybha nar shadidat altwhj, tusqa min eayn shadidat alhrar. lays li'ashab alnaar taeam 'iilaa min nbt dhi shwk lasq balard, wahu min shari altaeam wakhbthh, la yusmn bdn sahibuh min alhuzal, wala ysdd jweh wrmqh"
  88,3,"wujuh alkufaar yawmayidh dhlylt baledhab, mjhdt bialeamal mtebt, tsybha nar shadidat altwhj, tusqa min eayn shadidat alhrar. lays li'ashab alnaar taeam 'iilaa min nbt dhi shwk lasq balard, wahu min shari altaeam wakhbthh, la yusmn bdn sahibuh min alhuzal, wala ysdd jweh wrmqh"
  88,4,"wjwh alkufaar yawmayidh dhlylt baledhab, mjhdt bialeamal mtebt, tsybha nar shadidat altwhj, tusqa min eayn shadidat alhrar. lays li'ashab alnaar taeam 'iilaa min nbt dhi shwk lasq balard, wahu min shari altaeam wakhbthh, la yusmn bdn sahibuh min alhuzal, wala ysdd jweh wrmqh"
  88,5,"wjwh alkufaar yawmayidh dhlylt baledhab, mjhdt bialeamal mtebt, tsybha nar shadidat altwhj, tusqa min eayn shadidat alhrar. lays li'ashab alnaar taeam 'iilaa min nbt dhi shwk lasq balard, wahu min shari altaeam wakhbthh, la yusmn bdn sahibuh min alhuzal, wala ysdd jweh wrmqh"
  88,6,"wjwh alkufaar yawmayidh dhlylt baledhab, mjhdt bialeamal mtebt, tsybha nar shadidat altwhj, tusqa min eayn shadidat alhrar. lays li'ashab alnaar taeam 'iilaa min nbt dhi shwk lasq balard, wahu min shari altaeam wakhbthh, la yusmn bdn sahibuh min alhuzal, wala ysdd jweh wrmqh"
  88,7,"wjwh alkufaar yawmayidh dhlylt baledhab, mjhdt bialeamal mtebt, tsybha nar shadidat altwhj, tusqa min eayn shadidat alhrar. lays li'ashab alnaar taeam 'iilaa min nbt dhi shwk lasq balard, wahu min shari altaeam wakhbthh, la yusmn bdn sahibuh min alhuzal, wala ysdd jweh wrmqh"
  88,8,"wjwh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,9,"wujuh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,10,"wjwh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,11,"wjwh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,12,"wjwh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,13,"wjwh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,14,"wujuh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,15,"wjwh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,16,"wjwh almuminin yawm alqiamat dhat nemt; lisaeyiha fi aldunya baltaeat radiatan fi alakhrt, fi janat rafieat almakan walmkant, laa tasmae fiha kalimat laghw wahdt, fiha eayn tatadafaq myahha, fiha surur ealiat wa'akwab mueadat llsharbyn, wwsayd msfwft, alwahidat janb alakhra, wbusut kathirat mfrwsht"
  88,17,"afla yanzur alkafirun almkdhdhibwn 'iilaa al'ibl: kayf khuliqat hdha alkhalq alejyb? wa'iilaa alsama' kayf rufieat hdha alrrafe albdye? wa'iilaa aljibal kayf nusbt, fhsl biha althbat llard walastqrar? wa'iilaa al'ard kayf busitt wmuhhidt?"
  88,18,"afla yanzur alkafirun almkdhdhibwn 'iilaa al'ibl: kayf khuliqat hdha alkhalq alejyb? wa'iilaa alsama' kayf rufieat hdha alrrafe albdye? wa'iilaa aljibal kayf nusbt, fhsl biha althbat llard walastqrar? wa'iilaa al'ard kayf busitt wmuhhidt?"
  88,19,"afla yanzur alkafirun almkdhdhibwn 'iilaa al'ibl: kayf khuliqat hdha alkhalq alejyb? wa'iilaa alsama' kayf rufieat hdha alrrafe albdye? wa'iilaa aljibal kayf nusbt, fhsl biha althbat llard walastqrar? wa'iilaa al'ard kayf busitt wmuhhidt?"
  88,20,"'afala yanzur alkafirun almkdhdhibwn 'iilaa al'ibl: kayf khuliqat hdha alkhalq alejyb? wa'iilaa alsama' kayf rufieat hdha alrrafe albdye? wa'iilaa aljibal kayf nusbt, fhsl biha althbat llard walastqrar? wa'iilaa al'ard kayf busitt wmuhhidt?"
  88,21,"feiz -ayha alrswl- almerdyn bima 'ursilt bih 'ilyhm, wala tahzan ealaa 'ieradhm, 'iinama 'ant waez lhm, lays ealayk 'ikrahhm ealaa al'iyman"
  88,22,"feiz -ayha alrswl- almerdyn bima 'ursilt bih 'ilyhm, wala tahzan ealaa 'ieradhm, 'iinama 'ant waez lhm, lays ealayk 'ikrahhm ealaa al'iyman"
  88,23,"lkn aldhy 'aerid ean altadhkir walmaweizat wasrr ealaa kfrh, fayueadhibuh allah aleadhab alshadid fi alnar"
  88,24,"lkn aldhy 'aerid ean altadhkir walmaweizat wasrr ealaa kfrh, fayueadhibuh allah aleadhab alshadid fi alnar"
  88,25,"'inn 'iilayna marjieuhum baed almwt, thuma 'iina ealayna jza'hm ealaa ma emlu"
  88,26,"'inn 'iilayna marjieuhum baed almwt, thuma 'iina ealayna jza'hm ealaa ma emlu"